{% doc %}
  Normalizes Arabic tanween al-fath: converts "اً" (fathatan placed on the
  alef) to "ًا" (fathatan on the preceding letter, before the alef). Use for
  dynamic, store-sourced text (product/collection/menu titles) where the
  tanween can't be corrected by hand.

  @param {string} text - The text to normalize

  @example
  {% render 'tanween', text: product.title %}
{% enddoc %}
{{- text | replace: 'اً', 'ًا' -}}
